## REST API ENDPOINTS (ApiController.cs)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

ApiKeyMiddleware:
  Read "X-Api-Key" header → match ProjectEnvironment.ApiKey (IsActive=true)
  Inject into HttpContext.Items["Environment"]
  No match → 401 JSON { "error": "Invalid API key" }

GET /api/client/features
  Header: X-Api-Key: {apiKey}
  Flow: Redis check → miss → load flags+groupMembers from DB → cache 30s → return
  Response:
  {
    "environment": "production",
    "projectSlug": "my-project",
    "fetchedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "flags": [{
      "name": "awesome-feature",
      "isEnabled": true,
      "description": "...",
      "targetMode": "SpecificUsers",
      "targetIdentifierType": "Email",
      "targetUserList": ["ali@co.com"],
      "groupMembers": []
    }]
  }

POST /api/client/metrics
  Header: X-Api-Key: {apiKey}
  Body: { "flagName": "...", "wasEnabled": true, "userId": "u1" }
  Action: upsert FlagEvaluationMetric (5-min bucket), update flag.LastSeenAt
  Response: 200 OK

